OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778767871
OL,3,CSix from hantavirus cruise ship leave
OL,4,Chospital to begin self-isolation
OL,6,FITV News' Emma Sweeney reports from
OL,7,Foutside of Arrowe Park hospital.
OL,9,FSix people who were on the cruise ship
OL,10,Flinked to an outbreak of hantavirus
OL,11,Fhave left Arrowe Park Hospital on the
OL,12,FWirral to continue their isolation at
OL,13,Fhome, health officials have said.
OL,15,FPassengers from the MV Hondius were
OL,16,Ftaken to the facility for checks by
OL,17,Fspecialists.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778767871
OL,3,CSix from hantavirus cruise ship leave
OL,4,Chospital to begin self-isolation
OL,6,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,7,Fsaid public health and clinical
OL,8,Fspecialists have assessed each
OL,9,Fperson's circumstances and after their
OL,10,Flatest negative test they are being
OL,11,Fallowed to continue their 45-day
OL,12,Fisolation at home.
OL,14,FIt said there are "appropriate public
OL,15,Fhealth protections in place at every
OL,16,Fstage of the journey" for those
OL,17,Fleaving the facility.
OL,26,@vD@SOUxD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778767871
OL,3,CSix from hantavirus cruise ship leave
OL,4,Chospital to begin self-isolation
OL,6,FHealth protection teams across the UK
OL,7,Fwill continue to monitor and support
OL,8,Feveryone after they leave the hospital
OL,9,Fthrough daily contact, it added.
OL,11,FThe UKHSA said all those at Arrowe
OL,12,FPark "remain asymptomatic".
OL,14,FThe agency praised the "incredible
OL,15,Fdemonstration of international efforts
OL,16,Fto contain the outbreak".
OL,18,FThe UKHSA said a medic on Ascension
OL,19,FIsland in the South Atlantic has
OL,20,Fdeveloped symptoms but has tested
OL,21,Fnegative.
OL,26,@tD@FOUtD@ZO]vD@XOUxD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778767871
OL,3,CSix from hantavirus cruise ship leave
OL,4,Chospital to begin self-isolation
OL,6,FFurther tests are being carried out to
OL,7,F"establish whether this is an
OL,8,Funrelated illness".
OL,10,FOn Tuesday it was announced that 10
OL,11,FBritons from South Atlantic islands
OL,12,Fconnected to the cruise ship outbreak
OL,13,Fare to be brought to the UK in case
OL,14,Fthey develop the illness.
OL,16,FThe group, thought to be residents of
OL,17,Fthe UK overseas territories of St
OL,18,FHelena and Ascension, are being
OL,19,F"brought to the UK to complete their
OL,20,Fself-isolation as a precautionary
OL,21,Fmeasure", the UKHSA said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@RO]{D@AOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
