OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778767871
OL,3,CSix from hantavirus cruise ship leave
OL,4,Chospital to begin self-isolation
OL,6,FProfessor Robin May, chief scientific
OL,7,Fofficer at the UKHSA, said: "Our teams
OL,8,Fare working closely with FCDO
OL,9,F(Foreign, Commonwealth & Development
OL,10,FOffice) colleagues and leaders on
OL,11,FAscension Island to repatriate British
OL,12,Fnationals who are currently isolating
OL,13,Fon the island.
OL,26,@oD@]OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778767871
OL,3,CSix from hantavirus cruise ship leave
OL,4,Chospital to begin self-isolation
OL,6,F"Testing is under way to confirm the
OL,7,Fcause of illness for the person
OL,8,Fdisplaying symptoms and we will take
OL,9,Fall necessary action to support this
OL,10,Fperson and the wider island population
OL,11,Fwhilst continuing to protect public
OL,12,Fhealth in England and UK overseas
OL,13,Fterritories.
OL,15,F"Once again I must commend those who
OL,16,Fhave co-operated so selflessly with
OL,17,Fthe isolation arrangements at Arrowe
OL,18,FPark, and we are pleased that they
OL,19,Fwill now begin to return home to
OL,20,Fisolate after a very unsettling period
OL,21,Ffor all involved.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778767871
OL,3,CSix from hantavirus cruise ship leave
OL,4,Chospital to begin self-isolation
OL,6,F"Thanks also to the NHS and UKHSA
OL,7,Fcolleagues caring for them throughout
OL,8,Ftheir time there.
OL,10,F"Together this has been an incredible
OL,11,Fdemonstration of international efforts
OL,12,Fto contain the outbreak.
OL,14,F"Our priority remains to ensure
OL,15,Feveryone is safe and well supported,
OL,16,Fwherever they complete their
OL,17,Fisolation, and our teams will continue
OL,18,Fto work closely with all of those
OL,19,Faffected by this outbreak."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOU{D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
