PN,39708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778767871
OL,3,CSix from hantavirus cruise ship leave
OL,4,Chospital to begin self-isolation
OL,6,FSo far, 11 hantavirus cases have been
OL,7,Freported among people on the cruise,
OL,8,Fincluding three deaths.
OL,10,FNine of the 11 cases are confirmed,
OL,11,Fwith two more probable cases.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
